entries.journal_entry_description: Collect an experimental Old Republic droid module, a Strategy/Tactics Simulation Chip, that is installed in a droideka that was being studied at Stonewall Labs near Dee'ja Peak.
entries.journal_entry_title: Old Republic Droid Modules: The Droideka
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Droid Module 3: Looks like you'll have to disable the Old Republic droideka before you can acquire the Strategy/Tactics Simulation Chip.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Droid Module 3: Defeat the Droideka to Acquire It
entries.task03_comm_message_text: [BEGIN TRANSMISSION]: Please return to the RSF mainframe in Theed. [END TRANSMISSION]
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Theed and update the RSF mainframe information about acquisition of the Strategy/Tactics Simulation Chip.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Return to the RSF Mainframe in Theed
